txt.en: 'I am certain that there are enemies still out there in Osgiliath. Search the city and find these craven lurkers. We must clear the city of foes if we are to truly reclaim Osgiliath for Gondor.'
Mablung has asked you to defeat  enemies still lurking in Osgiliath.
'Good work. Though I fear there may be more. MÃ­rthel has spotted movement among the shadows on his watch. Still, you have made a dent! And yet we must not lower our guard.'
You should talk to Mablung, who can be found at the Ranger encampment in after-battle Osgiliath.
